title: JAVA code getter and setter extractor
author: Shahzad Malik
description:
Extracts all Getter and Setter from the entire Java Code , Eliminates all comments , commented and unused functions from code .
Provides raw data of code . 

Input : - ( Copy Paste entire java code in assethub UI )

Output :- the output variable is df .
df      :-   Provides dataframe of Variables and function name in which it is used
